<div class="nv-text text aem-GridColumn--tablet--12 aem-GridColumn--phone--12 aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--7">
 
 	
    <div id="nv-text-51069b388a" class="general-container-text            ">
			<div class="text-left lap-text-left tab-text-center mob-text-center">
				<div class="description ">
                	<p><span class="p--large">NVIDIA Alpamayo is an open portfolio of AI models, simulation frameworks, and physical AI datasets designed to accelerate the development of safe, transparent, and reasoning-based <a href="/glossary/autonomous-vehicles/" target="_self">autonomous vehicles</a>.</span></p> 
<p><span class="p--large">Built for Level 4 autonomy, Alpamayo lets vehicles perceive, reason, and act with human-like judgment, while providing the interpretability and openness required for <a href="/ai-trust-center/halos/autonomous-vehicles/">safety validation</a> and regulatory collaboration. The portfolio integrates seamlessly with the NVIDIA autonomous driving stack—from <a href="/solutions/autonomous-vehicles/ai-training/">training</a> and simulation to in-vehicle deployment—helping you move faster without building core autonomy infrastructure from scratch.</span></p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p>
